author: snoopdave
msg: Corrected query syntax. Also, the pubTime=pubTime,updateTime=updateTime updates, meant to prevent the database from resetting those two timestamp fields cause an error with OpenJPA.Turns out, they are unecessary here because OpenJPA takes care of preserving those value (tested that on MySQL and Derby).
